-family-design\",\n174 |     \"target\": \"Industries batch 4\",\n175 |     \"allowLandingChanges\": false,\n176 |     \"prompt\": \"Upgrade /industries/energy, /industries/telecom, /industries/government, and /industries/public-sector using the premium industry family design. Do not touch landing page. Energy challenges: asset operations, field service, regulatory documentation, grid or plant knowledge, operational optimization. Telecom challenges: network operations, customer service, field operations, knowledge fragmentation, service delivery visibility. Government/Public Sector challenges: citizen services, policy search, case workflows, documentation, transparency and governance. Suggested agents: Asset Operations Agent, Field Service Copilot, Document Intelligence Agent, Knowledge Search Agent, Executive Dashboard Agent, Network Operations Copilot, Customer Experience Agent, Citizen Service Agent, Policy Intelligence Agent, Case Triage Agent. Related platforms: TelecomVerse, Control Center, Runtime Governance. Avoid government or compliance guarantees. No fake clients, fake agencies, or fake metrics. Include rich visuals, tabs/carousels, architecture panels, and mobile responsive layouts. Run lint/build.\"\n177 |   },\n178 |   {\n179 |     \"id\": \"22-industries-batch5-professional-services\",\n180 |     \"title\": \"Design Audit Tax Legal Advisory pages\",\n181 |     \"scope\": \"page-family-design\",\n182 |     \"target\": \"Industries batch 5\",\n183 |     \"allowLandingChanges\": false,\n184 |     \"prompt\": \"Upgrade /industries/audit, /industries/tax, /industries/legal, and /industries/advisory using the premium industry family design. Do not touch landing page. Audit challenges: evidence collection, documentation review, risk assessment, workflow consistency, knowledge retrieval. Tax challenges: document-heavy workflows, knowledge search, advisory support, compliance tracking, client response time. Legal challenges: contract review, matter knowledge, 