ole, accompanied by a dynamic progress bar indicator.\n- **High-Quality Contextual CTAs**: Concludes with a premium CTA directing users to 'Connect with Engineers' and 'Explore Architecture Specs', fully consistent with GFF AI’s theme.\n\n### 3. Validation Done\n- Ran `npm run build` to verify standard static page generation and TS types compilation. The build completes perfectly in ~13.5s with zero errors or warnings.\n- Executed `npx eslint app/build/sandbox/page.tsx` directly to confirm code adherence to top-tier enterprise guidelines. The file passed cleanly with zero warnings or errors.\n- Verified mobile responsiveness via Tailwind fluid grid breakpoints and checked accessibility features on forms/buttons.\n\n### 4. Limitations\n- Entirely frontend-only (as requested by security/phase guardrails), avoiding fake servers, real backends, or chat-model API calls. All logs are stored and simulated deterministically.","verified":true}}}
